## Introduction to the Data

I first downloaded the `LakeHuron.csv`file as we have seen in class to my idyll data folder. I am using this data to create a visualization of the water level in Lake Huron over time. This interactive visualization allows you to view the relationship alone, or to view the water level changes by a redpurple color scheme by clicking the `Water Level` button. It is generated via
the file `index.idyll`. [Dataset Source](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UIUC-iSchool-DataViz/is445_spring2021/master/week10/data/LakeHuron.csv)

